txt.en: Eluna wishes for you to act as her escort for a critical meeting.
'I managed to arrange a meeting with one of the Draig-lûth. Hopefully we can sort this out without more violence, but should things take an unfortunate turn, your sword arm would be most welcome.'
You have returned to Lhan Garan with Eluna and the others.\n\nTalk to Eluna.
'If you are prepared, we should leave now.'
'That could have gone better, but it certainly could have gone worse.'
Eluna has arranged a meeting with the Draig-lûth.\n\nYou should talk to her when you're ready.
